Subject: Re: [T2] new engine in 71 bus will not start

Broken rotor??
Dirty points??
Unplugged or bad condenser??
Have someone turn the engine while you hold a grounded test light on the
coil terminal that goes to the condenser. If it flashes your points are
working, if not your problem could be there.
This is assuming throwing a new coil at it doesn't work.
Good luck
Brian
